 Copy the HTML code below.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="cach-lap-chi-muc-link-website-wordpress-tren-google-nhanh-nhat-03.jpg" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="How to index wordpress website link on google fastest 03" width="100%" height="100%" /></span></p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Step 4: Open the login process to your website </span><a href="https://wordpress.com/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://wordpress.com/</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">. <strong>Tool and Marketing</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="cach-lap-chi-muc-link-website-wordpress-tren-google-nhanh-nhat-04.jpg" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="How to index wordpress website link on google fastest 04" width="100%" height="100%" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Choose <strong>Trafic</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img title="cach-lap-chi-muc-link-website-wordpress-tren-google-nhanh-nhat-05.jpg" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="How to index wordpress website link on google fastest 05" width="100%" height="100%" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Paste the HTML code as shown below. Then save it.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="cach-lap-chi-muc-link-website-wordpress-tren-google-nhanh-nhat-06.jpg" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="How to index wordpress website link on google fastest 06" width="100%" height="100%" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight